Gargle Da Gangle

Players choose an unseen video from the youtube channel "deathbattles".

Players watch the explanation of the characters powers while playing the following drinking game.
If one of the following happens take 1 drink:

    - Someone curses
    - The word technically is said
    - Boomstick mentions his ex-wife
    - Boomstick mentions beer
    - Wiz is experimented on
    - Crude Joke / Sexist Comment is made

Once the character power explaination is done the drinking game ends.
Players then bet on the character they want to by choosing sides.

    If a player bets correctly => Gain 2pts
    Bet Wrong => Take 1 shot

Players can choose to double down before the fight starts. By doing so they get double the points if correct, 
but get double the shots if they loose.